#: ../../modules/cost_functions/cost_functions_model.rst:2
msgid "ModelCostFunction"
msgstr "ModelCostFunction"

#: ../../modules/cost_functions/cost_functions_model.rst:4
msgid ""
"The "
":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.model_cost_function.ModelCostFunction` "
"bridges classical optimization models with quantum result objects. It "
"accepts any :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model` (including convenience "
"subclasses such as :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`) and evaluates it "
"against measured bitstrings or the amplitudes of a final quantum state."
msgstr ""
"La classe "
":class:`~qilisdk.cost_functions.model_cost_function.ModelCostFunction` "
"fa de pont entre els models d'optimització clàssics i els objectes de "
"resultat quàntic. Accepta qualsevol :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model` "
"(incloent subclasses de conveniència com ara "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`) i l'avalua contra les cadenes de bits "
"mesurades o les amplituds d'un estat quàntic final."

#: ../../modules/cost_functions/cost_functions_model.rst:9
msgid ""
"When the provided model is a :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`, the cost "
"function automatically converts it into a Hamiltonian and computes the "
"expectation value. Otherwise, it maps each sample to the model's "
"variables, feeds them through :meth:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model.evaluate`,"
" and aggregates the resulting objective and constraint values."
msgstr ""
"Quan el model proporcionat és un :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO`, la "
"funció de cost el converteix automàticament en un Hamiltonian i calcula el "
"valor d'expectació. En cas contrari, mapeja cada mostra a les variables del "
"model, les processa a través de "
":meth:`~qilisdk.core.model.Model.evaluate`, i agrega els valors objectiu "
"i de restricció resultants."

